title: Harlequin Intrigue - November 2014 [epub]

Harlequin Intrigue brings you three new edge-of-your-seat romances for one great price, available now! This Harlequin Intrigue bundle includes Rustling Up Trouble by USA TODAY bestselling author Delores Fossen, Boneyard Ridge by Paula Graves and Cold Case at Cobra Creek by Rita Herron.

Harlequin Intrigue brings you three new edge-of-your-seat romances for one great price, available now! This Harlequin Intrigue bundle includes The Hunk Next Door by USA TODAY bestselling author Debra Webb and Regan Black, Crossfire Christmas by NEW YORK TIMES bestselling author Julie Miller and Night of the Raven by Jenna Ryan.

Catch a thrill with 6 new edge-of-your-seat romances every month from Harlequin Intrigue!
